Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.89,0:00:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放弃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.74,0:00:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊哟哟 一直冷静沉着的柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}脸可是急得红通通的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.55,0:00:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快 放马过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}右边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上当了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么会！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Yeah～那边是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呀 赢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呜 小柳生输了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那接下来就进入惩罚游戏环节吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咱家弹额头可是很痛的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}慢著 输的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要弹就弹我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是团体战 输了就得全体受罚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有什么可是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:00:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀…我对不起你…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.87,0:01:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好痛痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.89,0:01:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接下来就轮柳生了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.16,0:01:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好痛…好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城姐你好过分！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哼 云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}胜负的世界是残酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都是你的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都是因为有这种东西在！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直输就耍这种花招太卑鄙了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是肉搏我可不会输给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我说你们 安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过海风的味道可真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那咱家就来嗅嗅妙龄少女的体香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:01:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂…葛城姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要性骚扰了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.36,0:02:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊呀呀 这可真是芳香沁鼻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这下可以吃下三碗饭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀也要闻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:08.25,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小云雀…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我说你们啊！都说安静一点了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那里就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}海边修行地 忍者岛
Comment: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:34.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,OP校准帧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:41.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}消えない鎖 その手で壊して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:03:00.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}惑いに侵されて 心に潜めてた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:03.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}傷だらけの　錆びた刃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:05.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}暗雲に翳した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:10.79,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}弱さ認めぬまま 強くはなれないと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:13.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}知った日から　目覚め出した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.88,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}確かな熱に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:21.05,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}螺旋の様に 絡まる紅い罠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:28.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}REALを焼き付けて 彼方へ蹴散ちせ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:34.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}遥かな宙に　一瞬の閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:36.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}今 亂れ咲き　影を纏い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}朧雲に放て
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.93,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}信じる道は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:47.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}必ずこの手で切り拓くと誓い立てて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:52.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}見えない鎖 撃ち抜けmaze
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:55.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}You DON'T need to grieve anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:57.93,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Who can read the future? Know thyself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:04:00.37,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Ready now! Discern truth or false
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Break your world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:41.24,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}几重枷锁 手中破
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:03:00.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}困惑侵扰 心中隐匿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:03.03,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}斑驳疮痍 刀刃发锈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:05.49,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}却为暗云罩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:10.79,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}不堪羸弱 誓要更强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:13.46,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}自知起 更醒悟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.88,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}热忱之切实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:21.05,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}庞若螺旋 赤罠笼络
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:28.62,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}铭刻现实 掷向彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:34.12,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}远空迢遥 一瞬閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:36.98,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}绮丽绽放 犹纏暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.40,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}耀于朧云上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.93,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}所坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:47.54,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}誓以我手 开辟我路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:52.69,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}击穿那道 无形枷锁
