Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:10.81,Chapter,,0,0,0,,{\pos(880,558)\fad(1000,700)\c&HE3EFED&}临海修行·忍者岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里就是合宿的地方么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这可是能够匹敌文化遗产的古屋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是不是该说它太有文化积累了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}或者说是颇有古风？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对对…我说的就是那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是呢 毕竟是忍者的修行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像鬼屋一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别说出来 云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都明白 心照不宣罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这可是从江户时代起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}杰出忍者们积攒修行的忍家宅邸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能在这样的宝地修行就该开心得梦里都偷笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很抱歉 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为和我们预想有点不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就一不小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和鬼屋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:04:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就赶快开始修行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在开始么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太快了吧老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难得来趟海边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先让我们去换身泳装吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为第一项修行是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打扫这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}的确得要先打扫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不然感觉都住不下去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果这里全都要打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}至少得弄到傍晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难得来趟海边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}首先不该是海么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是啊…老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咱家可不是在偷懒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别吓人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咱家还以为是雾夜老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 雾夜老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他刚才好像说是要去钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟柳生一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 明明自己使唤我们来做扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且干嘛还叫上柳生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像是为了确保今天晚餐的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上钩了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:07:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好…这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可有伤我作为教师的体面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道说…晚餐材料…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要现捞么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概这也是训练的一环吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米饭 味噌还有盐姑且还是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不如说只有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目标 超级忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:21.21,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}目标 超级忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:21.22,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}我要加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这些柴火应该够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好想快点…看泳装啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还以为是白碗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}结果原来上面全灰尘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小飛鳥 那葱是哪来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}长在后面田里的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然有点快枯了 不过现在也不能奢求呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呐 小飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}超级忍者？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是这样写着的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会不会是以前到这儿的学姐写的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}写在那种不起眼的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也许是想写着玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以才在看不到的地方悄悄写上愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也不是不能明白那种心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊 愿望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}写的人有没有变成一名厉害的忍者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能成真就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}满载而归咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这么多…比平常还奢侈啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不愧是雾夜老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}开动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}柳生 我对你刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雾夜老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然我不擅长钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过贝壳可是我捞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}超级忍者是怎样的忍者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从名字来看 是超越所有忍者那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}类似…究极忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果有那样的忍者在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就能轻松收拾那群恶忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界搞不好就和平了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.01,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:46.22,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}海带对身体可是很好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍法·乱枕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍法·枕返
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀我也要！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小云雀 得分！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢你 小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小云雀有柳生的铜墙铁壁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咱们也来协力作战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}给我停下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}命中！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们是要挑战本小姐么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就接受你们的战帖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 你们当现在几点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次再吵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都没早饭吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}托你们的福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}害得我也受牵连了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这也是修行的一环
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生真是好喜欢小云雀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}毕竟是同一个年级嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}关系好是件好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比起说是因为同年级
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}倒不如说云雀像是柳生的妹妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟同学也早点睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天也要早起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}超级忍者是怎样的忍者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}超级忍者么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来了海边还得穿制服…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}当然了 我们可是来修行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 今天要进行“命驱”的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:50.30,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7}注：这里直译是拼上性命 为保证翻译风格和原作相同所以直接使用了命驱的写法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}“命驱”？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}“命驱”是指
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在战斗前自行解除忍者装束 破釜沉舟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}使速度和攻击力大幅提升的忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是在“命驱”状态下 防御力会急剧降低
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:25.96,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7}注：原作中 \N阴属性下命驱后攻击力变为原本的4.5倍 速度变为1.5倍 防御变为5分之1 \N阴乱属性的命驱则为攻击力7.5倍 防御10分之1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在“命驱”的状态下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敌人每一下攻击都可能造成致命伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算是可能被打中也得设法躲开！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 你们也试试
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总算到了休息时间啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呐 小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}刚刚就是穿着泳装修行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}干嘛要再特地换次衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那和这不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用来战斗的泳衣和用来看的泳衣可不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城 把我的泳衣还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又没有别人在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.10,0:14:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真空上装也不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}玩乐也是修行的一环
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还我啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:14:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没看到雾夜老师么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我没看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我还想找老师确定一下明天的日程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:19.23,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7}在那座山崖等你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:19.23,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7}您重要的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好多鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呐 小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有这么多鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然上面来了命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就姑且陪你玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 论逃跑的本事你倒是挺厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你…你是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恶忍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛇女子学园一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}给我记住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}俺绝对不会放过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要伤害云雀的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}尽管放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H486BA3&\blur4\bord8}忍·转身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你够强么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}强？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我倒希望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过既然要执行命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有力量怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咱家等这一刻可等了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H1B13EF&\blur8\bord4}忍·转身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明多多少少有命中到啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是…凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可能 凛已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}调虎离山！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟糕 学生们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这点小伤不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小看我可得遭殃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&H0D04AF&\bord4\blur8}必死之宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\c&H000000&\3c&H0D04AF&\bord4\blur8\pos(640,650)}Sterblich
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哼 今天就先这样饶了你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次再碰面时可没这么简单了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}给我记住了！
Comment: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}#（未来你的四次元裙底又变得更厉害了啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这个人到底是来干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但她的本事可比看起来的强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}汝真弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就先这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跑哪去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还没分出胜负来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一个人都没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}出什么事了么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被算计了么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛇女子学园
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她们是这么说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您知道么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前些日子刚从半藏大人那里听说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}秘立蛇女子学园
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是与我们半藏学园相对的恶忍培训机构
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恶忍？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}培训机构？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我本想在这次修行里告诉你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那之前袭击我的那位也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}商店街的傀儡使也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}应该都是蛇女子学园的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像打从一开始就没想认真跟咱家决一胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被她戏弄了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真火大！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次再碰到绝不会放跑她！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}袭击我们的人也是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 感觉不到杀意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总之 她们做到这一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就不能认为是单纯的挑衅了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然还不知道她们的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但善忍绝不能向恶忍屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我都不会输的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}当然 下次一定要打赢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后好好地性骚扰一番
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}攻击我干嘛啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}结果还是变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这才像是葛城姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的 小云雀！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}差不多该是吃饭的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这边则是嘴馋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再多些紧张感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天的晚饭有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乌贼刺身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}烤乌贼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}炸乌贼脚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全是乌贼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有意见可以不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那副打扮…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么敵人会知道凛的事情
Comment: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ED FIRST
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:13.04,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}捧げた思いが冷えたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:19.35,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}氷の乙女になるんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:26.08,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}信じた願いが朽ちたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:33.56,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}戦う乙女になるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.59,0:22:40.23,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}あどけないと言われた頃に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:46.65,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}戻れないから　この身はさまよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:49.66,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}孤独の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:53.54,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}暗夜の悪しき者よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:57.07,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}誇り高く麗しく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:23:00.28,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}こころに香る花は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.79,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}震えまいと空に咲く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.79,0:23:06.96,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}暗夜の悪しき者よ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:10.49,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}誇り高く麗しく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:13.64,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}こころは赤い花よ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.64,0:23:17.17,ED-JA2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}摘み取られる前に散れ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:13.04,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}若是奉上的思念渐渐冷却
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:19.35,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我会变成一位庞若寒冰的女孩么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:26.08,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}若是坚信的愿望枯萎腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:33.32,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我会变成一位沉沦战斗的女孩么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.56,0:22:40.03,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}那段被人称作“天真无邪”的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:46.65,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}已经回不来了 所以我的肉身才会在此彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:49.66,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在这孤独之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:53.54,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}暗夜的邪恶之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:56.90,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}有我们的美学与荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.07,0:23:00.28,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在心中芬香的花朵儿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.56,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不惧颤抖要在空中绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:06.96,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}暗夜的邪恶之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.96,0:23:10.40,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}有我们的美学与荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:13.64,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}心中那朵赤红的花儿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.64,0:23:17.17,ED-CH2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}定要在被人摘取前凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}柳生还真是喜欢乌贼干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.37,0:23:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我当然还有别的爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你还喜欢什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.31,0:23:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀和乌贼干是排一起的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.91,0:23:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下回 奇袭！半藏学园
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:40.02,Chapter,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,484)\bord2\blur2\shad1\c&HE2EEEE&\3c&H383A3B&}奇袭！半藏学园
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拼上性命来相夺吧
